Zira Editor is a lightweight PHP Editor with syntax highlighting and autocomplete.

Main features:
- syntax highlighting for PHP, JavaScript, CSS, HTML
- autocomplete of PHP built-in functions and classes
- autocomplete for JS, CSS, HTML
- project support
- autocomplete of project classes, functions, variables
- unused variables highlighting (experimental)
- file symbols navigator
- built-in PHP manual (download required)
- git support
- sass support
- quick access panel
- search in files
- go to declaration
- built-in colorpicker

Tested on OpenSuSe Leap 15.0 with QT 5.9.4